text: Georgia Taylor (born Claire Marie Jackson; 26 February 1980) is an English actress. She is best known for portraying the roles of Toyah Battersby in the ITV soap opera Coronation Street (1997–2003, 2016–present), Ruth Winters in the BBC medical drama series Casualty (2007–2011), and Kate Barker in the ITV police drama series Law & Order: UK (2013–2014). She was born and raised in Wigan, Greater Manchester, United Kingdom. ==Other websites== * Category:1980 births Category:Living people Category:English television actors Category:English movie actors Category:Soap opera actors Category:Wigan Category:Actors from Greater Manchester
